<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA38">
<l>tāṉē taṉakkuvamaṉ ṟaṉṉuruvē yevvuruvun</l>
<l>tāṉē tavavuruvun tārakaiyun – tāṉē</l>
<l>yericuṭaru mālvaraiyu meṇṭicaiyu maṇṭat</l>
<l>tirucuṭaru māya viṟai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He’s comparable only to himself. His form is every form.</l>
<l>He is the form of penance, the stars is he,</l>
<l>the lord who is the flaming fire, the great mountains, the eight directions</l>
<l>and the two lights of the [cosmic] egg.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
